        INPUT:

        - ``G`` -- real matrix. Matrix is assumed to be lower triangular.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: from riemann_theta.riemann_theta import NormGramInt
            sage: RR = RealField(40)
            sage: G=matrix(RR,2,2,[1,2,2,1])
